item.content:encoded:
• Edit
  • Edit

EXQUISITE THAI
DINING

  • Edit

Voted San Francisco's Best Thai Restaurant

  • Edit
  • Edit

PERFECT FOOD HUB

  • Edit

Our hospitality begins at the door as you are welcomed into the light and airy multi-level space by a well-educated staff trained in the fine art of personalized attention. Upstairs, the two elegant dining rooms are comfortable and inviting.

  • Edit
  • Edit

SAVOUR FLAVOUR

  • Edit

The delicious hand made mille crpes and assorted cakes
are baked fresh daily

  • Edit
  • Edit
make a reservation
  • Edit
  • Edit
  • Edit
  • Edit

Embracing romance in San Francisco with a first, or second, date? Perhaps youre concerned that meeting for drinks is too casual but worried that an actual dinner date is too much pressure? Our elegant meze bar may be just what youre seeking for that upscale yet casual meeting.

From the quiet flamboyance of our chilled lobster cocktail to the understated yet graceful grape arugula salad, our staff can provide whatever is required to suit your mood and preferences. Our seafood is flown in daily giving our tuna tartare and grilled octopus an unmatched freshness.

Oysters have a long, historic association with romance, and we pride ourselves on our selection. Fresh selections from around the world are provided as options for the discerning diner, including Bluepoints and Wellfleets from the East as well as Kumamotos and Kushis from the West.

Taste sensational dishes such as our famed our lamb-chop lollipops, or add decadent duck baklava to the table. Either will give your afternoon meet-up a touch of luxury, especially when paired with our handcrafted cocktails.Time is a precious commodity, and life is too short to spend it on dining in a less than ideal atmosphere.

THE KITCHEN

ALVIN YEO

REFLEXOLOGY IN YOGA

  • Edit

MARCH 2018

  • Edit

Reflexology is an alternative medicine involving application of pressure to the feet and hands with specific thumb, finger, and hand techniques without the use of oil or lotion.

  • Edit
LEARN MORE
  • Edit
  • Edit
  • Edit

ACUPRESSURE MASSAGE

  • Edit

MARCH 2018

  • Edit

Acupressure is an alternative medicine technique similar in principle to acupuncture. It is based on the concept of life energy which flows through meridians in the body.

  • Edit
LEARN MORE
  • Edit
  • Edit
  • Edit

AYURVEDIC MASSAGE SESSION

  • Edit

MARCH 2018

  • Edit

Ayurvedic Massage known as Abhyangam in Sanskrit is one of the most common and important Ayurvedic therapies. It is an important regime to maintain a healthy lifestyle.

  • Edit
LEARN MORE
  • Edit

Why Yoga?

  • Edit
  • Edit

Practicing yoga is a great way to calm and focus your mind while improving balance, flexibility and overall body strength. Health is the prime concern today.

  • Edit
LEARN MORE
  • Edit

Rest & Relax

  • Edit
  • Edit

Yoga gives an individual relief from countless ailments at the physical level. The practice of the postures (asans) strengthens the body and creates a feeling of well being. From the psychological view point, yoga sharpens the intellect and aids in concentration. It steadies ones emotions as a bonus. Practicing breathing techniques (pranayam) calms the mind. In the realm of the spiritual, yoga brings awareness and the ability to be still. Through meditation inner peace is experienced.

  • Edit
LEARN MORE
  • Edit
  • Edit

Explore Peace

  • Edit
  • Edit

Meditation is the best way to take deep rest and be alert at the same time. It is a skill that calms the mind and allows you to get in touch with your inner self. It is the precious inner peace that is derived by meditating, by sitting still with ourselves for few minutes. The result of meditation is precious - it takes us to our Self - that too in just a few minutes.Today, meditation is seen as an effective remedy to deal with the stresses of daily life. To address the conflict in our mind and in society too.

  • Edit
LEARN MORE
  • Edit

Organic Cuisine

  • Edit
  • Edit

Everything absorbed by five senses like Mouth (food, water), Nose (Breath), Ear (Chanting, sweet music), Skin (Sunlight), Eyes (Nature) is Food. When we consume food in adequate amount, it gives us long life and youthfulness. When consumed in inadequate amounts, it increases production of toxins which is harmful for life. Having right food is the initial step towards achieving healthy life. But just having right food is not enough. Right combination and proportion of food is also important for an individual.

  • Edit
LEARN MORE
  • Edit
  • Edit

Revitalize Your Focus

  • Edit
  • Edit

Focus is an inbuilt natural function. It is possible to enhance it naturally simply by relaxing the mind. While you may have personal choices to relax your mind, it may or may not necessarily sustain focus. To sustain focus, it is imperative to relax the mind through meditation.

  • Edit
LEARN MORE

item.title: About Us
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
About Us

Our Company

Our mission is to provide the best services to the customers for their climbing adventure.

We provide professional experts to each trip or person so that our customers can take a sigh of relief.

With over 40+ years of experience specialized in rock climbing, ice climbing and many other climbing trips. Our main principles are to take you at new level of climbing adventures with safety.

David Otunga

Facebook Twitter Google-plus Skype

Titus O'Neil

Facebook Twitter Google-plus Skype

Meet the Owners

David Otungahas worked with the major brands of rock climbing. He also many awards for expertise in climbing. He had 25+ years of climbing experience.

Titus O'Neilis an ice climbing expert with an experience of about 20+ years. He complete his expertise with a certification from UIAA (Union Internationale des Associations d'Alpinisme).

+ Climbing Trips + Places Visit + Years Of Experience $ Tours Sold + Happy Clients

item.title: Services
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Services

Girls Climbing

We offer trips and tours for girls also, so they can enjoy the adventure of climbing at their own comfort. We also have female climbing experts for these trips.

Ice Climbing

Some clients wants to go for ice climbing with their friends and families. So our organization provide them expert professionals for ice climbing trips.

Expert Climbers

We have a team of professional climbing experts with an experience of 25+ years. Our trainers provide best training and safety tips to every clients.

Rental Equipments

We also provide rental equipment to those clients who want to go climbing alone. We provide the best quality equipment to all clients for their safety.

Climbing Practices

Our inspection focuses on the safety and performance of the climber. We provide training services, safety tips and equipments to our clients before the trip.

Strength Checkup

We also provide health checkup to test the strength and level of stress of every client before the trip. Client's safety is the first priority of our organization.

+ Climbing Trips + Places Visit + Years Of Experience $ Tours Sold + Happy Clients

• Welcome To

    rock climbing Club

    We are dedicated to provide the best of adventures to our travellers.
    Explore the world heights with us. Our Services

  • Welcome To

    Rock challenging tours

    Leave all your worries,meet new people, have starry night conversations
    & have the time of life, with Us. Our Services

  • Welcome

    Be Our Guests

    Come & have the experience of your life with us.
    We are the best in what we do. Our Services

Climbing

Trekking

Exploring

Rapelling

Rope Climbing

Rock Climbing

Expert Climbers

Our mission is to provide the best services to the customers for their climbing adventure.
We provide professional experts to each trip or person so that our customers can take a sigh of relief.
With over 40+ years of experience specialized in rock climbing, ice climbing and many other climbing trips. Our main principles are to take you at new level of climbing adventures with safety.

Book Your Trip

Get on with us & experience the best of adventures today. Book now and get a chance to experience the best trip
secured with expert professionals & dedicated personnel.

    Our Adventures

    We believe in providing the best services to keep our clients happy and keep up
    to their expectations of having a lively experience with us.

    Rappelling

    We take you to high rise cliffs for rappelling. These are private properties so you don't have to wait in any queues for your turn.No trees are damaged & you can climb rocks with our super experienced professionals.

    Rock Climbing

    High rock adventures on beautiful sandstone cliffs. All types of cliffs from 35 feet to just under 100 feet. We offer fully guided tours for the all our customers.Join us today for an enthralling experience.

    Eco Tours

    Discover nature rocks with the best Eco tours held by us. Enjoy the guided nature hike, fern covered forests, surrounded by amazing rock formations, & learn about the geology of the area & much more.

    Our Customers Reviews

    Choose and learn from our clients and their enthralling experiences.
    We are proud to serve our clients.

    Michael Peter

    I proudly said to everyone that i am able to climb at any peak. This could only happen because of training experts of your organization.

    Michael Peter

    I would love to climb at every high altitudes to reach my limits of inspiration. I had my own personal guide provided by your organization is very good.

    Michael Peter

    During the climbing trip, I and my friends always feel cheerful, adventurous and safe because we have professional climbing experts with us.

    Our Expert Team

    We have a fully experienced and well equipped team comprising of expert professionals
    who are dedicated to make it a lifetime and safe experience for you.

    Jacob William

    Jacob is an A-certified expert in rock climbing. He imparts his expertise to our clients and guides them throughout the journey.

    Facebook Twitter Google-plus Pinterest

    Charlie James

    Charlie is our tour guide,equipped with great amount of knowledge about nature and its activities.He is there to impart information about trees, etc.

    Facebook Twitter Google-plus Pinterest

    James Thomas

    James is our rappelling expert. He has been climbing rocks and hills since a lot of years for now. He is well versed with all the casualities and their solutions.

    Facebook Twitter Google-plus Pinterest

item.title: Rock Climbing With Safety Equipments
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: We are the leading organization that gives our customers full climbing enjoyment with appropriate safety measures. For us, customers safety is our priority task. We also provide safety tips to every climber and weassign a professional with every group.For an emergency situation, we have a support team of experts that helps customers at every point.

item.title: Climb Alone And Reach Heights
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Every person wants to reach the heights alone by pushing their limits. We have a proper solution for this because we have a team of experts that gives you training for climbing alone. We also provide personal trainers for those who want to go alone for climbing, but we also provide safety measures to them and also prepare a backup team for emergency situations.
